Du hc Anh l im n uy tn v m bo chun v cht lng ca h thng gio dc. Mc d so vi h thng gio dc Vit Nam, gio dc Anh c s khc bit vi Vit Nam, v d Ph thng Vit Nam l 12 nm, i hc 4 nm th bn Anh theo h GCSE, Alevel v ln i hc 3 nm,... nhng vi s h tr ca cc trung tm t vn nh Sunrise Vietnam, s khc bit ny khng cn l ro cn cho ph huynh v hc sinh la chn du hc Anh.

Cc trng Ni tr trn hin ang c chng trnh hoc bng cho hoc sinh Vit Nam thng qua Sunrise vi tri gi t 20% n 50% cho ca hoc ph v sinh hoat ph v hoc bng tri gi t 50% n 100% hoc ph cho chng trnh GCSE v A Level.

Sunrise Vietnam thng bo
tuyn sinh
+ Hc bng ton phn.
+ Hc bng chnh ph cho cc chng trnh hc ting, i hc, Thc S v Tin S ti Trung Quc.
+ Hc bng ph hp cho cc bn hc sinh ang hc lp 12 tr ln (i vi bc i hc) v ang hc nm cui i hc (i vi bc Thc s) v hon thnh Thc s (i vi bc Tin S), khng cn c ting Trung trc.

Theo thng k ca B Gio Dc Trung Quc, ngy cng c nhiu sinh vin nc ngoi n y hc tp. Hin nay, Hn Quc l nc c nhiu sinh vin theo hc ti Trung Quc nht vi hn 60,000 sinh vin. Tip theo l M, Nht Bn, Nga, Indonesia, n v cc nc Chu u nh Php, c. Du hc Trung Quc c u im l chi ph thp, nhng vi nhng sut hc bng ton phn hay hc bng chnh ph th vic du hc ti y cn hp dn hn nhiu ln. Th t ln bn tnh, bn s thy sau khong thi gian hc ti Trung Quc, bn c bng cp, c ngoi ng ting Trung, v khon tin tit kim c bn c th u t hc thm ting Anh. y l l trnh bo m cho bn mt vic lm hoc 1 s nghip pht trin sau khi ra trng.

hn np h s: thng 4/2016

c 3 loi hc bng vi nhiu u vit nh sau:

hc ting 1 nm hoc hc ting + i hc 4 nm

hc bng ton phn hc ph i hc trung quc (1 nm ting + 4 nm i hc)

hc bng chnh ph 1 nm ting + bc thc s, tin s (2 n 4 nm)
du hc nht ti thnh ph niigata
vi chi ph hp l, th tc n gin

Thnh ph giao lu quc t Niigata vi dn s khong 810 nghn ngi, c cng nhn l thnh ph ln nht pha b bin Nht Bn, do l cu ni rt gn n cc nc nh Trung Quc, i Loan, Hn Quc, Nga v Hawai.

T Niigata cchTokyo 1,5 ting bng tu tc hnh. T sn bay Niigata c cc chuyn bay thng n cc nc trn th gii. Thm vo tnh Niigata c bit n l tnh c go ngon nht Nht Bn, c thin nhin phong ph nh bin, ni, rng v c tn hng s thay i ca bn ma. Nhn t kha cnh an ton v v vt gi th y l mi trng an ton cho du hc sinh yn tm hc. Niigata cn ni ting l thin ng truyn tranh Manga ni sn sinh ra nhiu tc gi truyn tranh ni ting tiu biu nh Mizushima Shinji vi truyn ''Dokaben'', Takahashi Rumiko vi truyn "Inuyasha".

Hc tp v sinh sng ti Niigata gip hc sinh tit kim c na chi ph sinh hot so vi Tokyo, cha k kh nng u visa gn nh tuyt i. Sunrise Vietnam xin gii thiu 3 trng Nht ng cho php chuyn tip ln cao ng, i hc d dng ti Niigata:
- Trng Ngn ng Quc t
- Trng Cao ng Hng khng, du lch ngoi ng quc t, khoa ting Nht
- Trng Cao ng Anime v Manga Nht Bn, khoa ting Nht
